data.description: With a location less than a mile to Depot Town this awesome Ranch  features 3 bedrooms (4th non-conforming in basement), 1 bath, partially finished basement, good sized fenced back yard with patio, new roof in 2020, high efficiency furnace less than 10 years old, A/C new in 2018, new windows in 2011 with transferable warranty, Hot Water heater within the last 5 years, this home is move in ready and waiting on you to create your new memories!
